title: Dan Bongino's Best of 2021: Donald Trump Returns
description:
I interview President Donald Trump about the $450k proposed payouts to illegal immigrants, the vaccine mandates, the growing China threat, elections in Virginia and New Jersey, and more.
One of my best interviews with him.
